{"id":12113,"date":"2024-02-21T18:20:25","date_gmt":"2020-07-21T12:50:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=12113"},"modified":"2023-11-03T19:18:47","modified_gmt":"2023-11-03T13:48:47","slug":"attic-home-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/attic-home-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"8 Beautiful Attic Home Design Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Attics can be used as study spaces, activity rooms or an extra bedroom in your home. Here are attic home design ideas for you.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you believe attics are awkwardly shaped spaces best used for storage, you are not alone. Many of us are guilty of ignoring this special place full of unmatched charm and warmth. Thanks to the advanced construction technology, today\u2019s attics are spacious and free from the cluttered look of older attics.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When remodeled correctly, your attic has the potential to be transformed into something special. From a teenager\u2019s room to a private home office, from a full-on studio to the children\u2019s activity room, your options to transform your attic into something useful, are endless.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out these beautiful attic design ideas from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> for some inspiration.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gift Yourself A Private Studio<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever imagined a private studio while planning your attic home design? This private studio is a slice of a quiet and beautiful heaven.&nbsp; The overall theme is grey, a neutral tone, and one that is relaxing that helps make a smaller space look and feel bigger. Also, if you have enough space, include a kitchenette in your studio.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173011\/attic-home-design-with-private-studio.jpg\" alt=\"Attic home design with a private studio\" class=\"wp-image-12117\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173011\/attic-home-design-with-private-studio.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173011\/attic-home-design-with-private-studio-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173011\/attic-home-design-with-private-studio-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173011\/attic-home-design-with-private-studio-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The skylights makes the studio feel brighter and lively<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Design A Teen Hangout Area<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Turning your attic area into a personalized and unique hangout area for your teens can definitely get you a \u2018Parent of The Year\u2019 Award. Add multiple sitting arrangements and of course a television as well as a music system for the party to keep going through the night! Yes, its perfect because you will be away from the noise and chatter your teenage kids will make.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172619\/attic-area-design-into-personalized-hangout-area.jpg\" alt=\"Attic area design into a personalised and unique hangout area for your teens\" class=\"wp-image-12114\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172619\/attic-area-design-into-personalized-hangout-area.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172619\/attic-area-design-into-personalized-hangout-area-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172619\/attic-area-design-into-personalized-hangout-area-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172619\/attic-area-design-into-personalized-hangout-area-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The brick wall and the colourful rug gives this attic a youth feel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Build An Isolated and Functional Home Office<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Want a private space to work from home? &nbsp;You can transform your attic space and design an interesting home office out of it. Select bright colours and detailing to have a comfortable and functional work area.&nbsp; Complete the space with a desk, chair and lots of shelves and drawers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173522\/isolated-functional-home-office-in-attic-design.jpg\" alt=\"Create an isolated and functional home office is an attic home design ideas\" class=\"wp-image-12122\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173522\/isolated-functional-home-office-in-attic-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173522\/isolated-functional-home-office-in-attic-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173522\/isolated-functional-home-office-in-attic-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173522\/isolated-functional-home-office-in-attic-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add some motivational posters and a whiteboard to complete the detailing<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go For An Attic Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What can be more ideal for a bedroom than an attic that is private, cosy, and romantic? This attic bedroom is especially a boon for those living in a joint family. Keep the furniture light and leave the corners empty to make the bedroom look larger and spacious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172729\/attic-bedroom-design-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Attic bedroom design ideas to make a private, cosy, and romantic\" class=\"wp-image-12115\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172729\/attic-bedroom-design-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172729\/attic-bedroom-design-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172729\/attic-bedroom-design-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21172729\/attic-bedroom-design-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A good view makes the morning special and ideal for private snuggle<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior solutions by india's most loved brand\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/03182406\/end-to-end-home-interior-solutions-by-indias-most-loved-brand.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Create A Children\u2019s Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Children love shapes and patterns and an attic in your home provides you with an opportunity to include both in their room. The vibrant wallpaper in the attic roof makes this bedroom look colourful. Check out how amazingly every corner of the room is used, to make this bedroom super functional?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173126\/childrens-bedroom-under-attic-home-design.jpg\" alt=\"Childrens bedroom design in attic area, wallpaper in attic roof makes this kids bedroom look colourful\" class=\"wp-image-12118\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173126\/childrens-bedroom-under-attic-home-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173126\/childrens-bedroom-under-attic-home-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173126\/childrens-bedroom-under-attic-home-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173126\/childrens-bedroom-under-attic-home-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The wooden flooring and the matching rug tie up everything together<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out<span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); font-size: revert; color: initial;\"> <\/span><a style=\"font-size: revert;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/kids-bedroom-design\/\">Kids Bedroom Designs by DesignCafe<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stay Fit With An Attic Home Gym<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Staying fit will become a hobby with a private gymnasium space you love. Convert your attic into an open, airy home gymnasium cum yoga studio. The space is a quiet escape from the rest of the home where you can blast loud music while you workout or get into a routine of relaxing yoga.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173256\/convert-attic-into-home-gym-cum-yoga-studio.jpg\" alt=\"Transform your attic into an open, airy home gym cum yoga studio\" class=\"wp-image-12119\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173256\/convert-attic-into-home-gym-cum-yoga-studio.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173256\/convert-attic-into-home-gym-cum-yoga-studio-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173256\/convert-attic-into-home-gym-cum-yoga-studio-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173256\/convert-attic-into-home-gym-cum-yoga-studio-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A dramatic colour scheme keep your motivation high all the time<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-gym-ideas\/\">Home Gym Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How About An Art Studio?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you one of those artistic types who need a private space to gather your thoughts and unleash your creativity? If yes, an attic with lots of natural light is perfect for your home art studio design. Ensure you add some storage space to keep your room neat and clutter-free.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173508\/home-art-studio-design-in-attic.jpg\" alt=\"Home art studio design in attic with lots of natural light perfect for art studio\" class=\"wp-image-12121\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173508\/home-art-studio-design-in-attic.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173508\/home-art-studio-design-in-attic-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173508\/home-art-studio-design-in-attic-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173508\/home-art-studio-design-in-attic-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Keep the colour palette neutral to give the space an airy feel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Design A Family Lounge<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Attic home design has unlimited possibilities. Add a comfortable couch and a large bookshelf and your private family lounge is ready. The large windows and the house plant gives the room a cosy feel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173405\/design-family-lounge-in-attic.jpg\" alt=\"Design a family lounge in attic to play games with your kids\" class=\"wp-image-12120\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173405\/design-family-lounge-in-attic.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173405\/design-family-lounge-in-attic-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173405\/design-family-lounge-in-attic-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/21173405\/design-family-lounge-in-attic-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Play games with your kids or spend time reading your favourite book<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Turning your attic into a usable space is a great idea especially for houses that are small in size. The space here is a bonus and you are free to convert into anything. Just put on your creative hat and get started.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-office-design-ideas\/\">Home Office Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-theatre-room-design-ideas\/\">Home Theater Room Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/nursery-design-ideas\/\">Nursery Des